OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled conditions prevail through
OL,7,Fthis period, with light winds and
OL,8,Fplenty of sunshine. A chance of a few
OL,9,Fshowers on Friday.
